    <item>
      <title>北京立法允许自动驾驶出租车，反对声不断升温</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/beijing-legislates-for-robotaxis-as-backlash-against-them-climbs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着高级驾驶辅助系统在中国变得越来越普及，北京将支持在城市网约车和汽车租赁车队中引入自动驾驶出租车。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/beijing-legislates-for-robotaxis-as-backlash-against-them-climbs</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 06:41:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>罗技拒绝创始人任命，拒绝新主席投票请求</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/logitech-snubs-its-founder-denies-request-for-a-new-chair-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[电脑配件制造商罗技国际公司 (Logitech International SA) 阻止了创始人丹尼尔·博雷尔 (Daniel Borel) 罢免董事会主席的努力，拒绝了他在 9 月 4 日的公司股东大会上提出的考虑更换董事会主席的请求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/logitech-snubs-its-founder-denies-request-for-a-new-chair-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 21:27:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>北约支持在发生海底袭击时通过重新路由到太空来拯救互联网的努力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/nato-backs-effort-to-reroute-internet-to-space-in-event-of-subsea-attacks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[北约正在帮助资助一个项目，该项目旨在寻找在欧洲海域传输民用和军事通信的海底电缆受到攻击时维持互联网运行的方法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/nato-backs-effort-to-reroute-internet-to-space-in-event-of-subsea-attacks</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 16:38:21 GMT</pubDate>
